{
  "title": "Sick-Day Brazilian Pork Back Ribs Stir-Fry",
  "description": "A comforting and flavorful sour, silky dish featuring pork back ribs that are perfect for a sick-day meal. This kosher-friendly recipe is sure to satisfy your cravings without overwhelming you.",
  "cuisine": "Brazilian",
